fields.description:
When specifying multiple media types in the function "showCamera" ( video & photo ), then you can only record a video. The switch between video and photo is not possible. On iOS it works.

*Tested on Nexus 9 /Android 6.0.1*

*Example:*
{code:java}
Titanium.Media.showCamera({
			saveToPhotoGallery : false,
			allowImageEditing : false,
			mediaTypes : [Ti.Media.MEDIA_TYPE_PHOTO, Ti.Media.MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO],
			videoQuality : Ti.Media.QUALITY_LOW,
			success : function(event) {
				. . .
			},
			cancel : function() {
				. . .
			},
			error : function(error) {
				. . .
			}
		});
{code}
